'''John Lithgow''' (born [[October 19]], [[1940s|1945]]),<ref name="Birth" /> best known for his many roles as a film and television actor, was the voice of [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] in the radio adaptations of [[The Empire Strikes Back (radio)|''The Empire Strikes Back'']] and [[Return of the Jedi (radio)|''Return of the Jedi'']].

